description:
Use 7zip to extract the files. The size is approx 769MB unpacked.


Note : the .iso is an exact image of the original GPL (version 1.0.0.0) which I bought back in 1998, it&amp;#039;s the FRENCH version. However you HAVE to install it through the separate installer otherwise it will simply NOT work on modern systems. The installer is the US version and will restore English language.


Install instruction :

-burn mount the .iso, do not install
-run the separate installer and follow the instructions
-the installer warns you about missing &quot;readme.txt&quot;, just skip it
-When done you may have a &quot;GPL NTFS Directory Check&quot; pop-up warning you about stuff. Don&amp;#039;t bother it&amp;#039;s bogus, the game runs just fine.
-restart your PC, play &amp; enjoy a hell of a sim





